spec_data.Name: glite-lb-server
spec_data.Description:
glite-lb-server is the gLite Logging and Bookkeeping server. This package
contains the L&B server daemon (glite-lb-bkserverd) and a tool for rebuilding
server indices (glite-lb-bkindex).
